				<title>Amazing</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12328278/scp-4707#post-4382837</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2019 00:25:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RoyalJudas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5622799</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The SCP alone isn't much to squeal about, but my god the programming and formatting! I was already impressed with the popups, the neural network feed responding to my mouse, and the page changing from safe to keter, but the real mind breaker for me was the detail in the inspect element console. You put so much work into this dude, this 100% gets a +1 from me. Bravo. Absolutely stunning.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
